Changelog for 'id3'.

2003-181 (W27):
  Code clean up + minor improvements (e.g. added [] to wildcard match)
  Bolted together (private) `id3' & (private) ID3v2 sources

2003-183 (W27):
  Started changelog.
  Install
  More code cleaning. Removed implementation-dependancy with rename()

2003-184 (W27):
  Readme
  Added specifying genre per number

2003-185 (W27):
  setid3v2.cpp:26: made w_ptr a live object + added bad_alloc checks
  setid3v2.cpp:90: void* src + ID3_free -> voidp<> src (exception safety)
  setid3.cpp:94: Now emits CR/LF pairs for %n, violating ID3v2, but
    conforming to Winamp. I figure more people care about Winamp.

